snippet.title: Fortnite Festival x The Weeknd - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Ladies & gentlemen… The Weeknd! The award-winning icon is the featured artist of Fortnite Festival Season 1: Opening Night. Learn more: https://fn.gg/Festival-S1

Play in a band with friends, perform solo, and create mixes with your favorite music by your favorite artists. Take your stage in Fortnite Festival!

Follow Fortnite Festival on social media:
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/fnfestival
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@fnfestival
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fnfestival
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fnfestival
